{
  "video_id": "EHNP7KqLrW4",
  "title": "Frederick Balagadde: Bio-lab on a microchip",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "The greatest irony in global health"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "is that the poorest countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "carry the largest disease burden."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "If we resize the countries of the globe"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "in proportion to the subject of interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "we see that Sub-Saharan Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "is the worst hit region by HIV/AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "This is the most devastating epidemic of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "We also see that this region"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "has the least capability in terms of dealing with the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "There are very few doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "and, quite frankly, these countries do not have the resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "that are needed to cope"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "with such epidemics."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "So what the Western countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "developed countries, have generously done"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "is they have proposed to provide free drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "to all people in Third World countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "who actually can&#39;t afford these medications."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "And this has already saved millions of lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "and it has prevented entire economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "from capsizing in Sub-Saharan Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "But there is a fundamental problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "that is killing the efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "in fighting this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "because if you keep throwing"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "drugs out at people"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t have diagnostic services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "you end up creating a problem of drug resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "This is already beginning to happen in Sub-Saharan Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "The problem is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "what begins as a tragedy in the Third World"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "could easily become a global problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "And the last thing we want to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "is drug-resistant strains of HIV"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "popping up all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "because it will make treatment more expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "and it could also restore"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "the pre-ARV carnage of HIV/AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "I experienced this firsthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "as a high school student in Uganda."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "This was in the 90s"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "during the peak of the HIV epidemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "before there were any ARVs in Sub-Saharan Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "And during that time, I actually lost more relatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "as well as the teachers who taught me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "to HIV/AIDS."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "So this became one of the driving passions of my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "to help find real solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "that could address these kinds of problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "We all know about the miracle of miniaturization."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "Back in the day, computers used to fill this entire room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "and people actually used to work inside the computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "But what electronic miniaturization has done"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "is that it has allowed people to shrink"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "technology into a cell phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m sure everyone here enjoys cell phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "that can actually be used in the remote areas of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "in the Third World countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "The good news is that the same technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "that allowed miniaturization of electronics"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "is now allowing us to miniaturize"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "biological laboratories."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "So, right now, we can actually miniaturize"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "biological and chemistry laboratories"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "onto microfluidic chips."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "I was very lucky to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "to the US right after high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "and was able to work on this technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "and develop some devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "This is a microfluidic chip that I developed."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "A close look at how the technology works:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "These are channels that are about the size of a human hair --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "so you have integrated valves, pumps, mixers and injectors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "so you can fit entire diagnostic experiments"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "onto a microfluidic system."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "So what I plan to do with this technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "is to actually take the current state"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "of the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "and build an HIV kit"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "in a microfluidic system."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "So, with one microfluidic chip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "which is the size of an iPhone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "you can actually diagnose"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "100 patients at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "For each patient, we will be able to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "up to 100 different viral loads per patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "And this is only done in four hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "50 times faster than the current state of the art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "at a cost that will be five to 500 times cheaper"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "than the current options."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "So this will allow us to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "personalized medicines in the Third World"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "at a cost that is actually achievable"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "and make the world a safer place."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "I invite your interest"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "as well as your involvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "in driving this vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "to a point of practical reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}